## Additional Context
- **Detached chat** uses `useDetachedChatWindow` and `useWindowStateSync`; keep cross-window logic centralized
- **Terminal panel** lives under `components/terminal`; keep shell/CLI logic out of chat modules
- **Provider settings** are per-provider (not global); UI must reflect provider capabilities
- **Tool approvals** are configurable per-tool (auto/deny/prompt); respect user preferences
- **Context usage** tracking with visual indicators (cold/yellow/red thresholds)
- **Thread persistence** includes full token/context usage in SQLite
